Package de.feig.FEDM.Core.ReaderConfig Description

Version 5.00.00

Copyright © FEIG ELECTRONIC GmbH, All Rights Reserved.

The data exchange between an application and the data container for reader configuration parameters in the reader class is realized with overloaded methods which passes a string from the package de.feig.FEDM.Core.ReaderConfig representing the name of the configuration parameter. All names of reader configuration parameters of all OBID® readers are unified and divided in hierarchical order in groups and subgroups separated by a dot.

For more general information, please refer to the system manual of the Reader.
